cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use CASTA in academic work, please cite it as below."
title: "CASTA - Contact Angle and Surface Tension Analyzer (drop-shape analysis tool)"
abstract: >-
  A desktop application (Python, Tkinter, OpenCV) for drop-shape analysis from
  images and videos: sessile-drop contact angle and pendant-drop surface
  tension, with scale calibration, ROI/baseline selection, and profile fitting.
type: software
authors:
